## 3. Acceptable Use

By using Shitposter, you agree:

* Not to use the App to harass, bully, threaten, or promote hate.
* Not to spam, flood, or otherwise disrupt servers.
* Not to use the App for illegal activities.
* To respect the rules of any Discord server where you use Shitposter.

We want the App to be fun. Don’t ruin it for others.

